This function can be used to retrieve the alpha-blending state. If it returns <tt>true</tt> then alpha-blending is enabled, and if it returns <tt>false</tt> it is disabled. By default this is on and so the function will return <tt>true</tt>
The above code checks the state of the alpha blending and if it is disabled it is then enabled again.
